      "representative_excerpt": "In terms of delegated entities and PBMs needing to make consumers fully aware of financial implications of the total cost of care when choosing a tier 1 versus a tier 2 or tier 3 medication, one example is gene therapies for rare disease.<br/>Types of gene therapies which need price transparency include but are not limited to:<br/>AAV gene therapies<br/>CRIS...",
