      "representative_excerpt": "I lead the employee benefits function for a multibillion dollar multinational with over 32,000 covered lives in the US. I've also lead benefits at 2 other large, publicly traded multinationals, had a long consulting career and worked for health plans. Further transparency documents and reporting will not control costs - very few of our participants read thes...",
