      "representative_excerpt": "FHIR based interoperability for pharmacy can enhance fee transparency for PBM disclosure and has the potential to improve quality outcomes via the MLR quality improvement activities for PDPs.<br/><br/>Pharmacy workflows for real time stock availability, fill status updates to prescribers, and pharmacy-to-pharmacy are still not ubiquitous.<br/>",
